* Table of Contents :toc:

* Basic idea

- tiling window manager
- minimal
- writen in C
- writen using xcb
  - Tutorial: https://xcb.freedesktop.org/tutorial/
  - Usage: https://xcb.freedesktop.org/usingxcb/
  - Example: https://github.com/mcpcpc/xwm
+ maybe implement bar like dwm (xsetroot -name)

* Memo

Do the fricking basics first, before implementing advanced features
e.g. get a window drawn before anything else is considered

* Compilation

+ Compile using:
#+BEGIN_SRC sh
 gcc zwm.c -o zwm -lxcb
#+END_SRC
